  "text": "Our results concurred with those by Dudok et al. [CITATION_1] in 2015, which mentioned that human LSCs proliferated in tissue culture without the support of HAM. The ex vivo analysis revealed that the optimum dose of AMEED for LSC culture was 0.1 mg/ml and in vivo analysis indicated that the optimum dose in the rabbit model was 1 mg/ml.",
